What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Oncology Information Systems Market?



Market Analysis and Size

The global oncology information systems market is expected to witness significant growth during the forecast period. This software predicts treatment outcomes, plans treatment, and exchanges cancer patient information across healthcare organizations. These benefits improve the safety and efficacy of cancer treatment for patients. OIS assists physicians and surgeons in selecting the most appropriate therapy to improve the survival rates of cancer patients. Hence, it is of great importance to market growth.

